arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Các bạn cần chuẩn bị những vật dụng sau để bắt đầu trồng rau muống:</span></span></p> <ul style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: none; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Hạt giống: hạt giống rau muống Phú Nông, Trang Nông...</span></span></li> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Chậu trồng rau: thúng xốp, thùng nhựa, khay ghép thông minh</span></span></li> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Đất trồng: đất thịt, đất dinh dưỡng...</span></span></li> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Phân bón: phân trùn quế, phân bò....</span></span></li> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Vị trí đặt khay trồng rau</span></span></li> </ul> <div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Sau đây mình bắt đầu trồng theo các bước sau:</span></span></div> <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-size: 16px; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">1. Ngâm hạt giống</span></span></strong></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">&nbsp;Nhằm đảm bảo hạt giống nảy mầm đạt tỉ lệ cao nhất trước khi gieo, bạn nên ngâm và ủ hạt giống</span></p> <ul style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; list-style: none; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Pha nước theo tỷ lệ 2 sôi + 3 lạnh khoảng 45-50ºC sau đó&nbsp;ngâm&nbsp;hạt giống&nbsp;khoảng 5-6h .</span></span></li> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Khi&nbsp;ngâm&nbsp;xong vớt&nbsp;hạt giống&nbsp;ra ngoài rồi ủ vào vật có mặt bằng phẳng như đĩa , đã trải sẵn khăn giấy ướt hoặc khăn vải ướt 6-8h.</span></span></li> <li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Đảm bảo&nbsp;hạt giống&nbsp;luôn ẩm, khi&nbsp;hạt giống&nbsp;nứt nảy mầm ta đem phơi khô 30 phút rồi gieo trồng.</span></span></li> </ul> <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-size: 16px; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">2. Chuẩn bị đất trồng</span></span></strong></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Tùy thuộc vào loại chậu hoặc khay trồng rau bạn sử dụng mà chuẩn bị lượng đất phù hợp.</span></span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: Roboto, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Kanit, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; user-select: initial !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background: transparent; font-weight: inherit; outline: 0px; vertical-align: top; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;">Sau khi ước lượng được lượng đất cần thiết bạn sẽ trộn đất với phân trùn quế hoặc có thể bổ sung thêm phân bò hoai để tăng thêm dinh dưỡng cho đất trồng.&nbsp;Thế là chúng ta đã làm xong khâu chuẩn bị đất để bắt đầu cho một vườn rau sạch đến khi thu hoạch được rồi.</span></span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; background-image: